!define MUI_WELCOMEPAGE_TEXT "Wan2GP Desktop is a desktop wrapper application for Wan2GP - the video/image/audio AI generation tool.$\r$\n$\r$\nIt installs and manages Wan2GP, so you can launch, update, change settings, and browse generated files - all from the Desktop app.$\r$\n$\r$\n$\r$\nOnce installed, you can:$\r$\n  > Launch Wan2GP right from the Desktop app$\r$\n  > Open Wan2GP in your browser instead$\r$\n  > Update and upgrade components$\r$\n  > Browse and preview generated images/videos$\r$\n$\r$\nThis is a TEST BUILD - for testing only, may be unstable."
